    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "Mrs. Arza Porter",
        "entity_key": "aport",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "arrived yesterday from "
      },
      {
        "text": "Huasna Ranch",
        "entity_key": "huasma",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ". She comes in response to information that "
      },
      {
        "text": "Mrs. M. Sparks",
        "entity_key": "mrssparks",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ", her mother, was seriously ill. We are glad to know that "
      },
      {
        "text": "Mrs. Sparks",
        "entity_key": "mrssparks",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "is better today."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "Steamer Santa Rosa",
        "entity_key": "sh_srsteamer",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "is reported due at 3:15 this afternoon from "
      },
      {
        "text": "San Francisco",
        "entity_key": "ci_sf",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ". She has thirty passengers and fifty-one tons of freight for "
      },
      {
        "text": "this city",
        "entity_key": "ci_sb",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ". "
      },
      {
        "text": "The steamer",
        "entity_key": "sh_srsteamer",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "goes south this evening at 6:30."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "The Ojai",
        "entity_key": "ojai",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": ", usually quite accurate, repeats the note which appeared in "
      },
      {
        "text": "the Press",
        "entity_key": "sbnewspress",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "relative to the metamorphosis of the little animal which is eating the grain on the "
      },
      {
        "text": "Hope Rancho",
        "entity_key": "hoperanch",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ". "
      },
      {
        "text": "Dr. Yates",
        "entity_key": "lya",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "published in those columns a full account of the little animal that was scientifically accurate. "
      },
      {
        "text": "Bro. Masick",
        "entity_key": "bromas",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "didn't seem to \"catch on.\""
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "At the "
      },
      {
        "text": "Opera House",
        "entity_key": "sbopera",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "last night, the "
      },
      {
        "text": "Wilber company",
        "entity_key": "wilber",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "presented the highly sensational comedy drama Shadows of a Home. The dialogue of the play is extremely interesting and held the attention of the audience to the end of the last act. The comedy scenes are very catchy and pleased the large audience immensely. The costuming was appropriate and costly, and the piece gave the best of satisfaction.—"
      },
      {
        "text": "Topeka Capital",
        "entity_key": "topekadailycap",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "The Ojai",
        "entity_key": "ojai",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
        "text": "says Joaquin Miller's novelette concerning the "
      },
      {
        "text": "Woman of San Nicolas",
        "entity_key": "lw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "has started the coast papers to telling what they know (or don't know) of the matter. \"The San Francisco Examiner and the Santa Barbara Press and INDEPENDENT have all come out lately with versions, but the article by "
      },
      {
        "text": "Dr. Lorenzo G. Yates",
        "entity_key": "lya",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "of "
      },
      {
        "text": "Santa Barbara",
        "entity_key": "ci_sb",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ", published in the "
      },
      {
        "text": "INDEPENDENT",
        "entity_key": "dailyindependent",
        "entity_type": "org"
      },
      {
