    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "A gentleman",
        "entity_key": "sbgentleman",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "of "
      },
      {
        "text": "this city",
        "entity_key": "ci_sb",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "took a walk down on the beach yesterday afternoon. He went over and beyond "
      },
      {
        "text": "Castle Rock",
        "entity_key": "castlerock",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ". About two or three hundred yards ahead were a couple of men standing near the bluff and enjoying shooting at a target of stones placed near the tide. As "
      },
      {
        "text": "the Barbareño",
        "entity_key": "sbgentleman",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "walked along he suddenly felt his hat move and a buzz at his ear. A small bullet also dropped at his feet. The cause of this was probably, [sic] one of the shots had glanced from the target and had just expended its energy as it reached and touched the man's hat. There is too much shooting indulged in hereabouts. Some severe or fatal accident will be reported next. The beach, populated as it is every day by pleasure seekers, is no place for shooting matches."
